      <title>工党计划周五召开关键会议，敲定英国大选提案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/labour-plans-crunch-meeting-friday-to-finalize-uk-election-offer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党将于周五在一个秘密地点举行关键会议，敲定其选举宣言的最终细节，但其与工会之间可能会就工人权利承诺发生争执。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/labour-plans-crunch-meeting-friday-to-finalize-uk-election-offer</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 18:28:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国内改革面临障碍，米莱取消 G7 峰会和马克龙访问</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/milei-cancels-g-7-macron-visits-as-reforms-face-hurdles-at-home</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱取消了下周前往意大利参加七国集团峰会的计划，并放弃了与法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙原定的会晤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/milei-cancels-g-7-macron-visits-as-reforms-face-hurdles-at-home</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 18:25:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>政治紧张局势致两名英国法官辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/hong-kong-court-sees-two-uk-judges-resign-amid-political-tension</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港持续推行国家安全镇压，压制国内异议，两名前英国法官辞去香港最高法院法官职务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/hong-kong-court-sees-two-uk-judges-resign-amid-political-tension</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 17:50:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乔治·桑托斯寻求今年夏天访问波科诺斯的许可</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/george-santos-seeks-permission-to-visit-the-poconos-this-summer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[面临刑事指控的前美国国会议员乔治桑托斯 (George Santos) 向审理其案件的法官请求允许他今年夏天前往波科诺山脉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/george-santos-seeks-permission-to-visit-the-poconos-this-summer</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 17:25:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗指责西方对核武器的担忧“具有误导性”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/iran-accuses-west-of-misleading-concerns-over-nuclear-weapons</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗指责德国、法国和英国威胁可能撤销 2015 年核协议中给予的一些制裁救济，导致紧张局势升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/iran-accuses-west-of-misleading-concerns-over-nuclear-weapons</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 17:00:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亨特·拜登向情人承认自己是个“酒鬼和瘾君子”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/hunter-biden-admitted-to-lover-he-was-a-drunk-and-an-addict</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亨特·拜登的前情人在枪支审判期间作证说，她经常恳求他去接受可卡因和酒精成瘾治疗，但他一直“像孩子一样逃跑”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/hunter-biden-admitted-to-lover-he-was-a-drunk-and-an-addict</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 16:30:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>史蒂夫·班农因藐视法庭罪被勒令 7 月入狱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/bannon-ordered-to-jail-by-july-as-he-fights-contempt-conviction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[史蒂夫·班农是前总统唐纳德·特朗普的长期顾问，他上诉推翻 2022 年藐视国会的判决失败，因此被勒令在 7 月 1 日前开始服刑四个月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/bannon-ordered-to-jail-by-july-as-he-fights-contempt-conviction</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 16:22:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议员蒂姆·斯科特将花费 1400 万美元为特朗普争取黑人选民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/senator-tim-scott-to-spend-14-million-wooing-black-voters-for-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南卡罗来纳州参议员蒂姆·斯科特是唐纳德·特朗普竞选搭档的头号候选人，他正在进行公开巡回演讲，向他的潜在老板展示他能为共和党总统候选人带来什么：黑人选民和亿万富翁捐助者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/senator-tim-scott-to-spend-14-million-wooing-black-voters-for-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 16:13:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>微软、英伟达将因人工智能举措面临美国反垄断调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/microsoft-nvidia-to-face-us-antitrust-probes-over-moves-in-ai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，美国正在对全球最有价值的两家公司微软公司和英伟达公司展开反垄断调查，原因是它们在快速崛起的人工智能领域占据主导地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/microsoft-nvidia-to-face-us-antitrust-probes-over-moves-in-ai</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 14:22:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>非洲人国民大会领导人举行会议讨论南非选项，祖马保持沉默</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/south-african-elections-anc-leaders-meet-on-coalition-as-zuma-stays-silent</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个月的选举未能产生绝对获胜者后，非洲人国民大会最大的决策机构召开会议，讨论如何与其他南非政党合作，总统西里尔·拉马福萨预计将在稍后提供有关审议情况的最新信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/south-african-elections-anc-leaders-meet-on-coalition-as-zuma-stays-silent</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 09:45:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
